Sentencas: The good oxygen ion conductivity makes brownmillerites suitable as electrode materials for SOFCs.
Titulo: Ca2Fe1.95Mg0.05O5: Innovative low cost cathode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: In this contribution, we focus on Ca2Fe1.95Mg0.05O5 (CFMO) with the idea of evaluating this brownmillerite as a promising innovative and low-cost cathode material.
Titulo: Ca2Fe1.95Mg0.05O5: Innovative low cost cathode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The synthesis was made through citrate route, where a magnesium doping was carried out to emphasize Fe3+/Fe4+ redox couple and thus the electronic conductivity.
Titulo: Ca2Fe1.95Mg0.05O5: Innovative low cost cathode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The chemical and physical properties of the material were verified by XRD, H2-TPR, XPS, BET and SEM techniques.
Titulo: Ca2Fe1.95Mg0.05O5: Innovative low cost cathode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The material was electrochemically characterized as a cathode by EIS, obtaining promising ASR values (0.19 [Icm2 at 800 degrees C).
Titulo: Ca2Fe1.95Mg0.05O5: Innovative low cost cathode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Furthermore, CFMO stability under different atmosphere conditions was confirmed by EIS investigation at different oxygen partial pressures.
Titulo: Ca2Fe1.95Mg0.05O5: Innovative low cost cathode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The material was activated by deposition of FeOx nanoparticles through co-deposition and infiltration; the effect of increasing amount (10 and 15 wt %) was also studied.
Titulo: Ca2Fe1.95Mg0.05O5: Innovative low cost cathode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The Ca2Fe1.95Mg0.05O5 based nanocomposites well perform as cathode materials and the electrocatalytic reduction of oxygen is enhanced by iron oxide.
Titulo: Ca2Fe1.95Mg0.05O5: Innovative low cost cathode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: This is confirmed by a reduction of ASR to 0.17 Ucm2 at 800 degrees C for CFMO with Fe2O3 15 wt % as the best result of the study.
Titulo: Ca2Fe1.95Mg0.05O5: Innovative low cost cathode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell
